%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Fire%20Engulfs%20Houses%20In%20Mumbai%2C%20Locals%20Use%20Buckets%20To%20Put%20It%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2015%20shops%20and%20houses%20were%20damaged%20in%20a%20massive%20fire%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20Mumbai%20early%20this%20morning.%20The%20fire%20erupted%20around%204%20am%20in%20Govandi's%20Baiganwadi.%20No%20injuries%20have%20been%20reported%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2015%20galas%20(commercial%20units)%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20and%20some%20houses%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20were%20damaged%20in%20the%20fire%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residents%20were%20also%20seen%20putting%20out%20the%20fire%20with%20buckets%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20engulfed%20electric%20wiring%20and%20installation%2C%20household%20items%2C%20AC%20sheets%2C%20plastic%20sheets%2C%20LPG%20cylinders%2C%20wooden%20planks%2C%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20cause%20of%20the%20fire%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20ascertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20more%20than%2020%20two-wheelers%20were%20damaged%20in%20a%20fire%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20an%20open%20parking%20lot%20in%20suburban%20Borivali.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708141080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fk6o7bmv8_mumbai-fire_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmassive-fire-breaks-out-in-mumbai-15-houses-damaged-5073428%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20ten%20to%20fifteen%20houses%20were%20damaged%20in%20a%20fire%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20Mumbai%20today%20morning%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmassive-fire-breaks-out-in-mumbai-15-houses-damaged-5073428%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmassive-fire