sofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fteri-baaton-mein-aisa-uljha-jiya-box-office-collection-film-inches-closer-to-rs-50-crore-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F107767277.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107767277.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Shahid%20Kapoor%20starrer%20is%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20an%20average%20film%20with%20its%20box%20office%20numbers%2C%20however%2C%20the%20budget%20is%20in%20place%20and%20with%20the%20money%20earned%20from%20the%20digital%20and%20satellite%20rights%2C%20it%20will%20be%20considered%20a%20good%20earner%20overall!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20NCP%20vs%20NCP%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Hints%20At%20Election%20Challenge%20Against%20Supriya%20Sule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20sounded%20the%20election%20bugle%20against%20Baramati%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20hinted%20at%20fielding%20a%20candidate%20against%20his%20cousin%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20segment%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20bastion%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20however%2C%20Maharashtra%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20announced%20his%20intent%20to%20field%20a%20candidate%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20also%20said%20that%20only%20if%20his%20candidate%20wins%20against%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20from%20Baramati%20and%20urged%20voters%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20said%20that%20he%20would%20field%20a%20candidate%20who%20has%20not%20contested%20an%20election%20earlier%2C%20but%20that%20person%20would%20have%20the%20support%20of%20those%20with%20ample%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20formation%20of%20Maharashtra%20state%20and%20the%20commencement%20of%20elections%20till%20date%2C%20it%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20Baramati%20that%20the%20deposit%20of%20opposition%20candidate%20was%20not%20forfeited.%20And%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20show%20their%20love%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20come%20to%20you%20and%20ask%20for%20your%20votes%20on%20emotional%20issues%20but%20it%20is%20up%20to%20you%20to%20decide%20whether%20you%20will%20vote%20on%20emotional%20grounds%20or%20to%20continue%20development%20work%20and%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20your%20future%20generations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20work%2C%20are%20bound%20to%20face%20allegations.%20Those%20who%20do%20not%20work%2C%20are%20bound%20to%20remain%20clean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narvekar%20backed%20his%20decision%20to%20declare%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Miniser%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20as%20the%20real%20NCP%20on%20Thursday%20by%20saying%20that%20no%20stand%20in%20the%20decision%20is%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Barbitrary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInteracting%20with%20the%20media%20a%20day%20after%20making%20the%20decision%2C%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20decision%20is%20very%20clear.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20decision%20has%20been%20provided%20to%20the%20parties.%20No%20stand%20in%20this%20decision%20is%20unconstitutional%20or%20arbitrary.%20The%20stand%20has%20been%20justified.%20Reasons%20for%20the%20same%20have%20been%20stated.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20further%20analyse%20such%20a%20tenable%20and%20justified%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Speaker's%20decision%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20the%20UBT%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20termed%20it%20a%20comedy%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20also%20allotted%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar%20held%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20assertion%20about%20vote%20share%20is%20not%20disputed%20by%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20legislative%20majority%20is%20also%20undisputed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar%20further%20dismissed%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20factions'%20pleas%20to%20disqualify%20MLAs%20after%20a%20vertical%20split%20in%20the%20party%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%206%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20while%20applying%20the%20test%20of%20majority%20in%20the%20legislative%20wing%2C%20ruled%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20was%20the%20real%20NCP%20and%20permitted%20the%20faction%20to%20use%20the%20'clock'%20symbol%20for%20the%20party.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708135740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv138fs0o_ajit-pawar-supriya-sule-ani_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-ncp-vs-ncp-ajit-pawar-hints-at-election-challenge-against-supriya-sule-5073281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20sounded%20the%20election%20bugle%20against%20Baramati%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20hinted%20at%20fielding%20a%20candidate%20against%20his%20cousin%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%