20company%20director%20in%20New%20York%20state%20for%20three%20years.%20His%20sons%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr%20and%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20have%20also%20asked%20to%20pay%20a%20fine%20of%20USD%204%20million%20each.%20They%20have%20been%20barred%20from%20serving%20as%20directors%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20and%20his%20two%20adult%20sons%20had%20already%20been%20found%20liable%20for%20massively%20increasing%20the%20value%20of%20their%20properties%20by%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20a%20trial%20that%20ended%20in%20January.%20However%2C%20Trump%20and%20his%20sons%20have%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20called%20the%20case%20a%20%26quot%3Bfraud%20on%20me%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20witch%20hunt.%26quot%3B%20Judge%20Arthur%20Engoron's%20decision%20came%20just%20weeks%20after%20closing%20arguments%20in%20the%20case%20following%20a%20months-long%20trial%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20general's%20office%20had%20requested%20the%20judge%20to%20ask%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20pay%20USD%20370%20million%2C%20which%20is%20USD%2016%20million%20less%20than%20ordered%20by%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20USD%201%20million.%20Weisselberg%20was%20also%20blocked%20from%20New%20York%20business%20for%20three%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Weisselberg%20and%20former%20controller%20Jeffrey%20McConney%20were%20banned%20for%20life%20from%20serving%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20financial%20control%20function%26quot%3B%20of%20any%20New%20York%20corporation%20or%20business%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20the%20independent%20monitor%20he%20installed%20to%20oversee%20Trump's%20business%20would%20continue%20functioning%20for%20three%20years%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20installation%20of%20an%20%26quot%3BIndependent%20Director%20of%20Compliance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20judge%20reversed%20the%20decision%20ahead%20of%20the%20trial%20that%20ordered%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20defendants'%20business%20certificates.%20Although%20the%20judge%20stated%20that%20the%20order%20could%20be%20renewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Hill%2C%20Trump's%20lawyer%20Alina%20Habba%20termed%20the%20ruling%20a%20%26quot%3Bmanifest%20injustice%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulti-year%2C%20politically%20fueled%20witch%20hunt%20that%20was%20designed%20to%20'take%20down%20Donald%20Trump.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20of%20the%20case%20lasted%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months%2C%20with%20testimony%20--%20sometimes%20tempestuous%20from%2040%20witnesses%2C%20including%20the%20former%20US%20President%20himself%2C%20top%20Trump%20Organization%20executives%20and%20Trump's%20adult%20children%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Hill%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20financial%20standing%20could%20face%20a%20major%20blow%20following%20the%20USD%20354.8%20million%20judgement%2C%20and%20another%20USD%2083.3%20million%20judgement%20against%20him%20for%20defaming%20writer%20E%20Jean%20Carroll%20after%20he%20denied%20her%20accusation%20that%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20decades%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708122660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8l68b4e8_donald-trump-afp_625x300_17_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-ordered-to-pay-354-million-in-new-york-civil-fraud-case-5072747%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20New%20York%20judge%20on%20Friday%20ordered%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20to%2