usinessinsider.com%2Fvideo-alexei-navalny-had-a-message-for-russians-if-he-died-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamed%20opposition%20leader%20Alexey%20Navalny.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It's%20unclear%20though%20how%20their%20tributes%20will%20translate%20into%20tangible%20action%2C%20especially%20on%20Congress'%20long-delayed%20push%20to%20send%20more%20aid%20for%20Ukraine's%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20international%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20clear%20that%20Putin%20will%20be%20met%20with%20united%20opposition.%26quot%3B%20But%20so%20far%2C%20Johnson%20has%20signaled%20that%20he's%20in%20no%20rush%20for%20the%20House%20to%20pass%20the%20Senate-led%20%2495%20billion%20aid%20package%20that%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20other%20conservatives%20oppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Congress%20debates%20the%20best%20path%20forward%20to%20support%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20our%20partners%20must%20be%20using%20every%20means%20available%20to%20cut%20off%20Putin's%20ability%20to%20fund%20his%20unprovoked%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20aggression%20against%20the%20Baltic%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20true%20that%20the%20foreign%20aid%20bill%20could%20garner%20218%20votes%2C%20getting%20the%20bill%20on%20the%20floor%20is%20another%20matter%20entirely.%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%2C%20a%20Georgia%20Republican%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAndrewSolender%2Fstatus%2F1747694818996662547%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20threatened%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20the%20same%20mechanism%20conservatives%20employed%20to%20boot%20then-Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20from%20power%20if%20Johnson%20passed%20more%20funding%20for%20Ukraine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20centrist%20Democrats%20have%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fhouse%2F4459157-adam-smith-mike-johnson-ouster-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20would%20protect%3C%2Fa%3E%20Johnson%20if%20such%20a%20challenge%20were%20to%20arise%2C%20but%20a%20GOP%20speaker%20remaining%20in%20power%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Democrats%20would%20be%20a%20politically%20dicey%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOvercoming%20the%20House%20GOP%20opposition%20hasn't%20and%20won't%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMcCarthy%20also%20left%20another%20conundrum%20for%20his%20successor.%20The%20California%20Republican%20made%20two%20key%20concessions%20to%20end%20the%20deadlock%20that%20allowed%20him%20to%20rise%20to%20what%20became%20his%20historically%20brief%20speakership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20now%20part%20of%20his%20political%20obituary%20%E2%80%94%20he%20allowed%20for%20any%20single%20lawmaker%20to%20raise%20a%20motion%20to%20vacate.%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz%2C%20a%20Florida%20Republican%2C%20took%20this%20power%20and%20used%20it%20in%20a%20historic%20moment%20that%20saw%20McCarthy%20kicked%20out%20of%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20concession%2C%20stocking%20the%20powerful%20House%20Rules%20Committee%20with%20staunch%20conservatives%2C%20continues%20to%20plague%20the%20House.%20Effectively%2C%20as%20Axios%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F01%2F18%2Fhouse-republicans-suspension-democrat-votes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20forces%20the%20House%20to%20pass%20almost%20any%20major%20legislation%20with%20two-thirds%20support%20or%20290%20votes%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20ways%20for%20Democrats%20and%20any%20supportive%20Republicans%20to%20blast%20through%20this%20de%20facto%20blockade.%20But%20there%20are%20costs%20to%20almost%20any%20procedural%20maneuver%2C%20and%20some%20require%20significant%20time.%20All%2C%20if%20Johnson%20remains%20opposed%2C%20would%20carry%20the%20political%20cost%20of%20asking%20the%20GOP%20to%20defy%20their%20leader%20and%20their%20colleagues.%20Trump%2C%20given%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20Senate%20bill%2C%20would%20likely%20apply%20pressure%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20Matt%20Glassman%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20Georgetown%20University's%20Government%20Affairs%20Institute%2C%20has%20emphasized%20that%20the%20question%20is%20not%20if%20there%20is%20power%20available%20to%20218%20lawmakers%20if%20they%20want%20to%20pass%20Ukraine%20aid%20but%20whether%20all%20of%20those%20lawmakers%20are%20united%20in%20the%20extent%20of%20just%20how%20far%20they%20will%20push%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20absolutely%20true%20that%20218%20(or%20216%20right%20now)%20in%20the%20House%20can%20force%20something%20onto%20the%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20Glassman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMattGlassman312%2Fstatus%2F1757410820017868971%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20earlier%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20stop%20them.%20But%20it's%20only%20if%20they%20have%20no%20other%20political%20considerations.%20Hellbent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentrist%20Republicans%20for%20the%20moment%20have%20said%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20support%20efforts%20that%20undermine%20Johnson.%20A%20small%20bipartisan%20group%20of%20House%20lawmakers%20has%20proposed%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fhouse-foreign-aid-bill-ukraine-israel-border%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20slimmed-down%20%2466.32%20billion%20%3C%2Fa%3Eproposal%20that%20would%20pair%20the%20defense%20aid%20with%20a%20legislative%20push%20to%20enshrine%20the%20Trump-era%20%26quot%3BRemain%20in%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20policy%20into%20law.%20(Congress%20can't%20recreate%20that%20policy%20on%20its%20own%2C%20the%20Mexican%20government%20would%20have%20to%20be%20involved.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECongress%20has%20a%20long%20to-do%20list.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20logistics%20that%20are%20difficult.%20Congress%20has%20lots%20of%20work%20after%20lawmakers%20return%20from%20their%20President's%20Day%20recess.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20will%20partially%20shut%20down%20on%20March%201%20if%20more%20funding%20isn't%20passed.%20Johnson's%20idea%20of%20dual-track%20funding%20means%20another%20deadline%20will%20follow%20soon%20after.%20The%20same%20day%20of%20the%20second%20funding%20deadline%2C%20March%208%2C%20there's%20another%20deadline%20for%20lawmakers%20to%20extend%20the%20FAA's%20funding%20authority.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-April%2C%20lawmakers%20must%20figure%20out%20the%20future%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Flive-updates%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fcongress%2Fspy-powers-pulled-johnson-00141510%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20Section%20702%20spy%20powers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Congress%20is%20also%20behind%20on%20the%20massive%20legislation%20that%20funds%20farming%20and%20food%20assistance%20programs%2C%20though%20lawmakers%20punted%20that%20to%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greatest%20example%20that%20this%20moment%20won't%20likely%20change%20anything%20came%20last%20year.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20came%20in%20December%20to%20make%20a%20last-minute%20plea%20to%20Congress%20to%20provide%20the%20funding%20his%20nation%20needs%20to%20repel%20Russia's%20invasion.%20Schumer%20compared%20him%20to%20Churchill.%20While%20a%20top%20Senate%20Republican%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgopers-say-zelenskyy-failed-to-persuade-them-on-ukraine-aid-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equestioned%20if%20he%20even%20moved%20the%20needle.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20we%20know%20the%20answer.%20Ukraine%20aid%20still%20hasn't%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexey-navaln-death-congre