aid%2C%20in%20his%20usual%20tongue-in-cheek%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20tulup%2C%20an%20ushanka%20and%20I%20will%20have%20valenki%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20traditional%20furry%20Russian%20winter%20coats%2C%20hats%20and%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20now%20live%20above%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20...%20But%20I%20don't%20say%20'ho-ho-ho%2C%20I%20say%20'oh-oh-oh'%20when%20I%20look%20out%20the%20window%2C%20where%20first%20there%20is%20night%2C%20then%20evening%2C%20then%20night%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20said%20he%20was%20tired%20from%20the%2020-day%20journey%20from%20his%20previous%20prison%20in%20the%20central%20Vladimir%20region%2C%20close%20to%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%20about%20me%2C%20everything%20is%20well.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20that%20I%20finally%20got%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Thinking%20about%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20after%20a%20spell%20in%20quarantine%2C%20Navalny%20shared%20more%20details%20about%20his%20conditions%20in%20the%20new%20Arctic%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20Putin%20was%20pleased%20(enough)%20that%20he%20had%20put%20me%20in%20a%20barracks%20in%20the%20Far%20North%20that%20they%20would%20stop%20throwing%20me%20in%20solitary%20confinement%20was%20...%20naive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2047-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrison%20authorities%20told%20him%3A%20%26quot%3B'Convict%20Navalny%20refused%20to%20introduce%20himself%20in%20the%20correct%20way'.%20Seven%20days%20in%20solitary%20confinement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20spent%20more%20than%20300%20days%20in%20solitary%20confinement%20--%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bpunishment%20cell%26quot%3B%20as%20his%20colleagues%20called%20it%2C%20based%20on%20its%20name%20in%20Russian%20--%20during%20his%20three%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20ordered%20there%20on%2027%20occasions%2C%20often%20for%20minor%20infringements%20of%20prison%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowed%20out%20for%20a%20daily%20walk%20in%20the%20pitch%20black%20of%20at%206%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20Navalny%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20promised%20myself%20I%20would%20go%20out%20in%20any%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20cell%20was%20%26quot%3B11%20steps%20from%20wall%20to%20wall%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20never%20been%20colder%20than%20minus%2032%20(Celsius).%20Even%20in%20such%20a%20temperature%20you%20can%20walk%20more%20than%20half%20an%20hour%20--%20only%20if%20you%20have%20the%20time%20to%20grow%20back%20a%20nose%2C%20ears%20and%20fingers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20January%209%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20I%20was%20walking%2C%20freezing%20and%20thinking%20about%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20and%20his%20trick%20with%20a%20dead%20horse%20in%20The%20Revenant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20scene%20in%20which%20his%20character%20crawls%20into%20an%20animal%20carcass%20to%20keep%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20would%20work%20here.%20A%20dead%20horse%20would%20freeze%20to%20death%20within%2015%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I'm%20Russian'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20also%20regularly%20ridiculed%20prison%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20he%20said%20the%20prison%20wardens%20at%20IK-3%20would%20wake%20everybody%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20to%20play%20the%20Russian%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20right%20after%20that%20--%20the%20second%20most%20important%20song%20in%20the%20country%3A%20Shaman's%20'Ya%20Russky%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20--%20which%20means%20%26quot%3BI'm%20Russian%26quot%3B%20--%20has%20become%20an%20unofficial%20anthem%20for%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20the%20scene.%20Yamal-Nenets%20region.%20Polar%20night.%20In%20a%20penal%20colony%20of%20convicts%2C%20prisoner%20Navalny%20serving%2019%20years%20--%20who%20the%20Kremlin's%20propaganda%20for%20years%20has%20scolded%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20Russian%20marches%20--%20is%20exercising%20to%20'Ya%20Russky'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Send%20me%20money'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20court%20hearing%20on%2015%20February%20--%20a%20day%20before%20his%20death%20--%20Navalny%20was%20filmed%20joking%20with%20the%20judge%20over%20a%20stream%20of%20fines%20he%20had%20been%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20honour%2C%20I%20will%20send%20you%20my%20personal%20account%20number%20so%20that%20you%2C%20with%20your%20huge%20salary%20as%20a%20federal%20judge%2C%20can%20send%20me%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20laughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20running%20out%20of%20cash%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20your%20decisions%2C%20it%20will%20run%20out%20even%20faster.%20So%20send%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20love%20you'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20last%20post%2C%20published%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20was%20dedicated%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Yulia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaby%2C%20you%20and%20I%20have%20everything%2C%20just%20like%20in%20the%20song%3A%20cities%2C%20airfield%20lights%2C%20blue%20snowstorms%20and%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20between%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20quoting%20a%20popular%20Soviet-era%20tune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20feel%20that%20you%20are%20near%20me%20every%20second%2C%20and%20I%20love%20you%20more%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708115460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fver9fqfo_alexei-navalny_625