0%26quot%3BPutin%20is%20responsible%20for%20Navalny's%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20was%20seeking%20more%20information%20about%20Navalny's%20death%20at%20a%20Russian%20penal%20colony%20north%20of%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%2C%20where%20he%20was%20dispatched%20less%20than%20two%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20has%20put%20a%20further%20chill%20into%20already%20bitter%20US-Russian%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2047-year-old%20Navalny%20had%20been%20a%20leading%20critic%20of%20Putin%2C%20and%20Biden%20had%20said%20after%20meeting%20Putin%20in%20Geneva%20in%20June%202021%20that%20Nalvany's%20death%20would%20risk%20devastating%20consequences%20for%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20and%20Putin%20remain%20deeply%20at%20odds%20over%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20Biden%20is%20urging%20Republican%20hardliners%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20to%20support%20additional%20funding%20to%20pay%20for%20more%20weaponry%20for%20Ukraine's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20figured%20prominently%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20as%20Biden%20seeks%20reelection%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20expected%20Republican%20opponent%2C%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20triggered%20bipartisan%20outrage%20last%20week%20by%20saying%20he%20would%20do%20nothing%20to%20defend%20NATO%20allies%20from%20Russia%20unless%20they%20paid%20a%20greater%20share%20for%20the%20common%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20Republican%20in%20Congress%2C%20House%20of%20Representatives%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20has%20not%20put%20a%20Senate%20bill%20for%20new%20funding%20for%20Ukraine%20up%20to%20a%20vote.%20After%20Navalny's%20death%2C%20he%20said%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20should%20use%20%26quot%3Bevery%20means%20available%20to%20cut%20off%20Putin's%20ability%20to%20fund%20his%20unprovoked%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20aggression%20against%20the%20Baltic%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Munich%20for%20a%20major%20security%20conference%2C%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20vowed%20that%20the%20US%20would%20never%20retreat%20from%20its%20NATO%20alliance%20obligations%20put%20in%20place%20after%20World%20War%20Two%2C%20contrasting%20Biden's%20approach%20to%20global%20engagement%20with%20presidential%20election%20hopeful%20Trump's%20isolationist%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20met%20with%20Alexei%20Navalny's%20wife%20Yulia%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20conference%20and%20%26quot%3Bexpressed%20her%20sorrow%20and%20outrage%26quot%3B%20over%20reports%20of%20her%20husband's%20death%2C%20a%20White%20House%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20presidential%20reelection%20campaign%20on%20Friday%20released%20a%20new%20minute-long%20advertisement%20blasting%20Trump%20for%20abandoning%20NATO.%20They%20planned%20to%20target%20the%20ad%20to%202.5%20million%20American%20voters%20in%20Michigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%20who%20trace%20their%20ancestry%20to%20the%20NATO%20states%20bordering%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708106520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffnubbsb8_joe-biden-reuters_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-responsible-for-russian-opposition-leader-alexei-navalnys-death-says-us-president-biden-5071824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Friday%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20surprised%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Boutraged%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20reported%20death%20of%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%20Alexei%20Navalny.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-responsible-for-russian-oppositio