%20different%20path%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20rebellion%20by%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20on%20Thursday%20held%20that%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20group%20was%20the%20real%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20when%20two%20factions%20emerged%20in%20July%202023.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20eight%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20on%20July%202%20last%20year%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-founded%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Satara%20in%20western%20Maharashtra%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20power%20comes%20and%20goes%20but%20ideology%2C%20policies%20and%20the%20thought%20to%20take%20the%20country%20forward%20are%20permanent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20some%20of%20our%20colleagues%20deviated%20from%20this%20path.%20Some%20took%20away%20the%20party%2C%20some%20took%20away%20the%20symbol.%20I%20never%20worry%20about%20all%20this.%20Some%20people%20chose%20to%20go%20on%20a%20different%20path%20by%20forsaking%20ideology%20but%20people%20did%20not%20appreciate%20this%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%26quot%3Bamusing%26quot%3B%20to%20hear%20from%20these%20persons%20that%20they%20left%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20work%20for%20development%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20can%20be%20in%20power%20all%20the%20time%20and%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20those%20who%20are%20not%20in%20power%20cannot%20serve%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAtal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%20several%20years.%20Did%20he%20not%20serve%20the%20country%3F%20Did%20he%20ever%20think%20of%20leaving%20his%20party%20to%20serve%20the%20country%20by%20leaving%20behind%20his%20ideology%3F%20Though%20we%20had%20our%20differences%2C%20one%20thing%20everyone%20has%20to%20accept%20is%20that%20he%20(Vajpayee)%20always%20preserved%20his%20ideology%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201977%2C%20when%20the%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20sat%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Was%20that%20a%20wrong%20decision%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20was%20facing%20farmers'%20issues%20but%20those%20in%20power%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%2C%20said%20Mr%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20session%20of%2015%20days%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20the%20Parliament%20only%20for%20one%20hour%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20it%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20or%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%2C%20they%20did%20not%20miss%20Parliament%20sessions%20even%20for%20one%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reference%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20routine%20swipe%20about%20his%20age%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%26quot%3BWe%20will%20overcome%20this%20situation%20too%20because%20if%20our%20ideological%20stand%20is%20strong%20then%20age%20will%20not%20make%20any%20difference.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20taken%20a%20decision%20to%20go%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20state%2C%20take%20the%20next%20generation%20along%20and%20create%20a%20new%20leadership%20to%20change%20the%20image%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2083-year-old%20opposition%20stalwart%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708104540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F53ri83jo_sharad-pawar_625x300_24_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-ajit-pawar-some-took-away-party-some-took-away-symbol-sharad-pawars-dig-at-nephew-5070969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar