n%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16183158%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-16-at-6.31.33-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2016%2C%20presented%20the%20state%20budget%20for%202023-24%20underlining%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20women%2C%20children%2C%20tribals%2C%20education%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20on%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%9CKarnataka%20model%20of%20development%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20allocated%20Rs%2086%2C423%20crore%20for%20gender%20budget%2C%20Rs%2054%2C617%20for%20children%20and%20Rs%2039%2C121%20crore%20for%20SCSP%20(Scheduled%20Caste%20Sub%20Plan)%20and%20TSP%20(Tribal%20Sub%20Plan).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20which%20was%20implemented%20last%20year%20as%20one%20of%20the%20guarantees%20promised%20during%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EAs%20on%20end%20of%20January%2C%201.17%20crore%20women%20have%20registered%20under%20the%20scheme.%20Rs.11%2C726%20crore%20has%20been%20directly%20transferred%20to%20the%20account%20of%20beneficiaries.%20In%20the%20year%202024-25%2C%20Rs.%2028%2C608%20crore%20is%20provided%20for%20this%20scheme.%20This%20money%20will%20support%20women%20to%20take%20up%20various%20income%20generating%20activities.%20It%20will%20also%20provide%20them%20with%20financial%20support%20for%20day-to-day%20household%20expenditure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20for%20early%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20of%20breast%20cancer%20and%20cervical%20cancer%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20announced%20in%20the%20budget%20that%20digital%20mammography%20machines%20will%20be%20provided%20to%2020%20district%20hospitals%20and%20colposcopy%20machines%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20K.C.%20General%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20district%20hospitals%20in%20three%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20Udupi%2C%20Kolar%20and%20Davanagere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESiddaramaiah%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20usage%20of%20menstrual%20cups%20will%20be%20promoted%20among%20women%20from%20SHGs%2C%20women%20members%20of%20Gram%20Panchayats%20and%20frontline%20workers%20of%20rural%20areas%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20will%20inspire%20other%20women%20in%20the%20villages.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20respect%20to%20the%20unorganised%20sector%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20a%20platform-based%20gig%20workers%20fund%20and%20welfare%20fee%20bill%20will%20be%20implemented%20to%20formulate%20welfare%20programmes%20for%20gig%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20women%20in%20Karnataka%20are%20allowed%20to%20travel%20for%20free%20in%20non-luxury%20public%20buses%20under%20the%20Shakti%20scheme%2C%20this%20time%20in%20the%20budget%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20announced%20a%20free%20bus%20pass%20scheme%20for%20rural%20journalists%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20district%20limits%20for%20their%20professional%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%C2%A0%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20also%20proposed%20that%20under%20the%20Anna-Suvidha%20ration%20programme%20senior%20citizens%20above%20the%20age%20of%2080%20years%20will%20also%20receive%20food%20grains%20at%20their%20doorstep.%20It%20was%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-karnataka-is-delivering-rations-to-people-aged-90-and-above%5C%22%3Eimplemented%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20for%20people%20aged%2090%20years%20and%20above.%20Further%2C%20Rs%201000%20incentive%20was%20announced%20to%20be%20given%20to%20caretakers%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20Cerebral%20Palsy%2C%20Muscular%20Dsytrophy%2C%20Parkinsons%20and%20Multiple%20Sclerosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20over%20three-hour%20long%20speech%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20quoted%20a%20song%20from%20Dr%20Rajkumar%E2%80%99s%20film%20%3Cem%3EBangarada%20Manushya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20diaolgue%20from%20recent%20Kannada%20hit%20movie%20%3Cem%3EDaredevil%20Musthafa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lingayat%20philosopher%20Aydakki%20Lakkamma%2C%20social%20worker%C2%A0and%20poet%20Ibrahim%20Sutar%20%2C%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Kuvempu%20and%20Basavanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncome-earning%20avenues%20for%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20announced%20that%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E50%20women-run%20cafes%2C%20called%20Cafe%20Sanjeevini%2C%20will%20be%20launched%20across%20the%20state%20during%20this%20year%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%207.50%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20canteens%20will%20cater%20to%20the%20demand%20and%20supply%20gap%20in%20rural%20areas%20for%20healthy%2C%20hygienic%20and%20affordable%20cooked%20food%20and%20traditional%20local%20cuisine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Coffee%20Board%2C%20one%20lakh%20women%20members%20of%20SHGs%20will%20be%20trained%20as%20coffee%20entrepreneurs%20and%202%2C500%20coffee%20kiosks%20managed%20exclusively%20by%20SHG%20women%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20Another%20major%20proposal%20is%20to%20develop%2050%2C000%20women%20SHG%20owned%20micro-enterprises%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20also%20mentioned%20that%20Savitribai%20Phule%20Women%20Empowerment%20Programme%20will%20be%20initiated%20in%20100%20select%20Gram%20Panchayats%20of%20the%20State%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skill%20training%20consistent%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20and%20interests.%20Moreover%2C%20cold%20press%20oil%20units%20will%20be%20established%20in%20all%20the%20Gram%20Panchayats%20of%20the%20state%20through%20the%20self%20help%20groups%20with%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs.1%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20the%20tribal%20communities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20budget%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20announced%20that%20Rs%2025%2C000%20monthly%20stipend%20will%20be%20given%20to%20100%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20research%20scholars%2C%20doing%20post%20doctoral%20fellowship%20and%2020%25%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20children%20of%2023%20nomadic%20and%20semi-nomadic%20communities%20in%20every%20residential%20school%20and%20a%20special%20cell%20will%20be%20established%20to%20provide%20ration%20card%20and%20other%20government%20documents%20to%20such%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20imbalance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20mentioned%20that%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20will%20be%20constituted%20to%20study%20the%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20measures%20taken%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%2022%20years%20based%20on%20Dr.%20D.M.%20Nanjundappa%20report.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20a%20new%20development%20index%20will%20be%20prepared%20by%20categorising%20districts%20and%20taluks%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20regarding%20economic%20and%20regional%20imbalance%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20D.M.%20Nanjundappa%20was%20formed%20to%20examine%20the%20regional%20imbalances%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20categorise%20the%20taluks%20based%20on%20cumulative%20development%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20emphasis%20on%20primary%20education%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20CSR%20grants%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20Karnataka%20public%20schools%20will%20be%20started%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20providing%20pre-primary%20to%20pre-university%20education%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20learning%20outcomes%20among%20school%20children%2C%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20announced%20two%20programmes%20%E2%80%93%20Ganitha-Ganaka%20programme%20and%20Marusinchana%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Ganitha-Ganaka%20programme%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20will%20collaborate%20with%20J-PAL%20Institute%20for%20students%20studying%20in%203rd%20to%205th%20standards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20programme%20is%20to%20make%20children%20like%20and%20learn%20mathematics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%C2%A0The%20proposed%20Marusinchana%20Programme%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20to%20improve%20the%20learning%20ability%20of%20students%20of%206th%20and%207th%20standard%20who%20are%20lagging%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNavu%20Manujaru%2C%20an%20interactive%20two-hour%20class%20involving%20discussion%20and%20debates%20will%20be%20conducted%20every%20week%20in%20all%20schools%20and%20colleges.%20These%20classes%20will%20promote%20ideas%20of%20social%20harmony%2C%20scientific%20temper%20and%20coexistence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20array%20of%20announcements%20related%20to%20the%20education%20sector%2C%20the%20government%20also%20announced%20that%20NEET%2FJEE%2FCET%20training%20programme%20will%20be%20organised%20for%20about%2020%2C000%20students%20studying%20in%20science%20stream%20in%20government%20pre-university%20colleges%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3ERead%20more%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finterim-union-budget-follows-tradition-of-modi-governments-apathy-towards-most-vulnerable%5C%22%3E%20Interim%20Union%20Budget%20Follows%20Tradition%20of%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Apathy%20Towards%20Most%20Vulnerable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraffic%20decongestion%20and%20trade%20and%20commerce%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20Sugama%20Sanchara-Brand%20Bengaluru%2C%20an%20expert%20organisation%20of%20international%20repute%20has%20been%20engaged.%20Based%20on%20their%20report%2C%20measures%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20ease%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20underlining%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20reduce%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20on%20a%20priority%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWidening%20of%20existing%20roads%20is%20difficult%20due%20to%20scarcity%20of%20land%20and%20problems%20in%20land%20acquisition.%20In%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20resolve%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20city%20by%20constructing%20underground%20tunnels.%20On%20a%20pilot%20basis%2C%20a%20tunnel%20will%20be%20constructed%20this%20year%20at%20Hebbal%20junction%20where%20there%20is%20high%20traffic%20congestion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20announced%20that%20shops%20and%20establishments%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20open%20till%201%20am%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%2010%20other%20corporation%20areas%20in%20order%20to%20further%20trade%20and%20commerce.%20This%20is%20a%20move%20which%20is%20welcomed%20by%20the%20business%20community%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fkarnataka-budget-shops-businesses-bengaluru-open-1-am-9165084%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUrban%20infrastructure%20development%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20announcements%20were%20made%20in%20order%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdecongest%20Bengaluru%E2%80%9D%20and%20develop%20other%20urban%20centres%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Nagar%20Vikas%20Yojana-2.0%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20provided%20for%20development%20of%20infrastructure%20in%2010%20Municipal%20Corporations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddara