SKM%20constituent%20BKU%20(Chaduni)%20group%20was%20active%20throughout%20the%20day%20by%20organising%20programmes%20at%20toll%20plazas%20and%20arterial%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20services%2C%20transportation%20and%20roads%20were%20the%20worst%20affected.%20Petrol%20dealers%20in%20Punjab%20closed%20filling%20stations%20to%20back%20the%20call%20for%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20the%20shutdown%20of%20shops%20and%20other%20establishments%20have%20been%C2%A0received%20from%20both%20urban%20as%20well%20as%20rural%20areas%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20Grameen%20Bandh%20call%20was%20different%20from%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20demonstration%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%2C%20as%20it%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20splinter%20group%20SKM%20(non-political)%20headed%20by%20convener%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20another%20forum%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20under%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20statement%20by%20SKM%20said%20that%20its%20Bharat%20bandh%20call%20was%20a%20day%20programme%20but%20it%20would%20intensify%20agitation%20in%20days%20to%20come%20till%20the%20time%20it%20achieves%20a%20law%20on%20MSP%2C%20loan%20waiver%2C%20and%20other%20key%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Grameen%20Bandh%20call%2C%20as%20per%20SKM%2C%20was%20in%20continuation%20of%20the%20demands%20for%20MSP%20at%20cost%2B50%25%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20reduction%20in%20input%20costs%2C%20debt%20waiver%2C%20repeal%20of%20Electricity%20(amendment)%20Bill%202022%20and%20no%20to%20prepaid%20meters%2C%20dismiss%20and%20prosecute%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20Union%20MoS%20(Home)%2C%20the%20main%20conspirator%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20massacre%20of%20farmers%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20stated%20that%20it%20has%20scheduled%20its%20Punjab%20Unit%20Meet%20on%20February%2018%20followed%20by%20its%20national%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20and%20general%20body%20meeting%20at%20New%20Delhi%20to%20suggest%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20statement%2C%20their%20strategy%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20already%20engaged%20in%20negotiations%20with%20SKM%20(non-political)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20and%20scheduled%20a%20fourth%20round%20of%20meeting%20the%20same%20day%20on%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bandh%20call%2C%20several%20SKM%20leaders%20asked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20and%20considerate%20to%20farmers%20who%20are%20suffering%20farm%20losses%2C%20distress%2C%20debt%2C%20and%20unemployment%2C%20while%20farm%20labour%20suffers%20severe%20hunger%2C%20failure%20of%20treatment%20and%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20them%2C%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20allegedly%20shown%20full%20sympathy%20to%20the%20corporate%20companies%2C%20but%20has%20%E2%80%9Cunleashed%20repression%E2%80%9D%20on%20farmers%20with%20lathi%20charge%2C%20pellet%20firing%2C%20tear%20gas%20sprays%2C%20use%20of%20drones%2C%20road%20blockade%2C%20house%20to%20house%20threats%20and%20continuing%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar-like%20approach%E2%80%9D%20towards%20the%20farmers%20involved%20in%20ongoing%20Delhi%20Challo%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20condemned%20even%20more%20vehemently%20the%20injury%20caused%20to%20several%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708099202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Froads-toll-plazas-shut-in-punjab-haryana-as-farmers-observe-grameen-bharat-bandh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20i