sh%2C%C2%A0had%20spent%20their%20exile%20from%C2%A0Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20the%20only%20Sita%20Temple%20in%20the%20whole%20of%20India.%20There%20had%20been%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20ground%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20new%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20a%20building%20called%20%3Cem%3ESita%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Es%20Kitchen.%3C%2Fem%3E%20But%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20spoken%2C%20after%C2%A0consecrating%C2%A0the%20Ram%20Statue%20in%20the%20new%20premises%2C%20of%20the%20need%20to%C2%A0create%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%20that%20embodies%20the%20virtues%20of%20a%20just%2C%20inclusive%20and%20compassionate%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20been%20befitting%20for%20an%20event%20which%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%20evoked%20in%20such%20terms%20and%20called%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%20to%20not%20only%20welcome%20back%20Ram%2C%20but%20also%20resurrect%20his%20consort.%20For%20far%20too%20long%20our%20Sitas%20have%20been%20buried%20under%20the%20furrows%20of%20the%20land%20to%20which%20she%20had%20retreated%20in%20order%20to%20save%20her%20honour%20as%20a%20wife%20and%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESita%E2%80%99s%20Sati%20had%20been%20a%20silent%20protest%20against%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20her%20by%20her%20spouse%20and%20king.%20To%20many%20women%20in%20India%2C%20throughout%20its%20long%20history%2C%20Sita%20has%20been%20seen%20not%20only%20as%20the%20model%20wife%2C%20but%20also%20as%20the%20archetypal%20victim%20of%20a%20male-dominated%20world.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20male%20pre-eminence%20remains%20the%20societal%20norm%20reserved%20to%20men%2C%20best%20represented%20by%20the%20figure%20of%20King%20Ram%2C%20and%20sanctified%20by%20his%20assigned%20divine%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20constitution%20was%20established%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20which%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20remembering%2C%20the%20current%20prime%20minister%20himself%20has%20called%20his%20%E2%80%98Gita%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equal%20rights%20of%20women%20have%20been%20enshrined%20and%20guaranteed.%20The%20foundation%20had%20thus%20been%20laid%20for%20a%20society%20that%20is%20neither%20patriarchal%20nor%20matriarchal%2C%20but%20based%20on%20the%20mutual%20respect%20of%20a%20shared%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symbolic%20framing%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98second%20Birth%20of%20the%20Nation%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20time%20not%20political%20but%20cultural%20and%20societal%20ruling%20elite%2C%20could%20have%20offered%20the%20chance%20to%20welcome%20back%20Sita%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20queen%20alongside%20her%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20been%20even%20more%20befitting%20if%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20inthronisation%20of%20Ram%20in%20his%20child%20avatar%20as%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20moreover%20at%20his%20very%20birthplace.%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20presence%20would%20have%20given%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20symbol%20of%20motherhood%20and%20to%20the%20essential%20role%20a%20mother%20plays%20in%20delivering%20a%20child%20and%20rearing%20it%20to%20full%20personhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20to%20be%2C%20and%20this%20erasure%20of%20constitutional%20Dharma%20reflects%20not%20only%20the%20male-dominated%20narrative%20of%20the%20whole%20Mandir%20movement%20and%20its%20apogee%20moment%2C%20the%20grand%20ceremony%20of%20January%2022%2C%202024.%20It%20also%20leads%20one%20to%20suspect%20(and%20fear!)%20that%20the%20Golden%20Future%20of%20Indian%20Society%20envisaged%20by%20the%20ruling%20elite%20remains%20trapped%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20it%20is%20not%20only%20the%20legal%20code%20of%20the%20constitution%20which%20directs%20society%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20male%20flag%20bearers%20%E2%80%93%20to%20give%20up%20their%20predominant%20role.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20historical%20duty.%20For%20far%20too%20long%20Indian%20and%20indeed%20global%20society%20have%20lived%20by%20the%20negative%20values%20that%20are%20rooted%20in%20male%20psychology%20%E2%80%93%20those%20of%20power%20and%20authority%2C%20of%20rivalry%20and%20the%20language%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20in%20my%20mind%C2%A0that%C2%A0this%20one%20factor%20has%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20its%20present%C2%A0predicament%2C%C2%A0riven%20by%C2%A0constant%20wars%2C%C2%A0by%C2%A0systematic%20violence%20against%20nature%2C%20and%C2%A0a%20climate%20of%20suspicion%20and%20envy%2C%20of%20fear%20and%20hate%20among%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResurrecting%20Sita%20from%20her%20grave%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20after%20%E2%80%98unearthing%E2%80%99%20the%20very%20spot%20of%20her%20birth-giving%20as%20the%20spiritual%20fulcrum%20%E2%80%93%20would%20have%20been%20a%20powerful%20symbol%20of%20healing%20for%20both%20men%20and%20women%20of%20India.%20It%20would%20have%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20shadows%20that%20besiege%20our%20society%2C%20proof%20of%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20poets%20and%20folk%20tellers%20have%20constantly%20given%20it%20expression%20in%20the%20many%20versions%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%20Katha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mere%20survival%2C%20viz.%20thriving%20of%20this%20myth%20through%20two%20millennia%2C%20is%20testimony%20enough%20that%20these%20shadows%20exist%2C%20and%20that%20they%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20To%20give%20this%20continuing%20erasure%20a%20symbolic%20focus%20point%2C%20Sita%20should%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20be%20given%20a%20sacred%20place%20of%20redemption%20in%20her%20honour.%20A%20new%20peaceful%20and%20respectful%20movement%20should%20start%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Etoday%20for%20every%20Sita%20to%20rise%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20every%20woman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJai%C2%A0Siyaram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERashna%20Imhasly-Gandhy%20is%20a%20psychologist%20and%20author%20of%20the%20books%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Psychology%20of%20Love%20%E2%80%93%20Wisdom%20of%20Indian%20Mythology%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Emerging%20Feminine%20%E2%80%93%20discovering%20the%20Heroine%20Within.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708095657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16175719%2Fimage-1840.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fin-rams-hailing-sita-was-forgotten-her-revival-would-have-symbolised-healing-for-men-and-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20many%20women%20in%20India%2C%20Sita%20has%20been%20seen%C2%A0not%20only%20as%20the%20model%20wife%2C%20but%20also%C2%A0as%20the%20archetypal%C2%A0victim%20of%C2%A0a%20male-dominated%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fin-rams-hailing-sita-was-forgotten-her-revival-would-have-symbolised-healing-for-men-and-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20hear%20Monday%20petition%20seeking%20annulment%20of%20February%208%20polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708095356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107760451%2Cimgsize-531173.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpak-supreme-court-to-hear-monday-petition-seeking-annulment-of-february-8-polls%2Farticleshow%2F107760296.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107760296.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPakistan's%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20hear%20a%20petition%20on%20Monday%20requesting%20the%20annulment%20of%20the%20recently%20held%20general%20elections.%20