.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20252%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20and%20needs%20296%20members%20to%20send%20all%20its%20eight%20candidates%20to%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDA%20currently%20has%20a%20strength%20of%20277%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%20(252)%2C%20Apna%20Dal%20(S)%20(13)%2C%20NISHAD%20(6)%20and%20SBSP%20(6).%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fup-rajya-sabha-poll-to-go-down-to-wire-as-bjp-plans-to-fight-8th-seat%2Farticleshow%2F107732695.cms%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20will%20need%2019%20additional%20votes%20to%20send%20all%20its%20candidates%2C%20and%20even%20with%209%20MLAs%20from%20the%20RLD%20and%20two%20from%20Jansatta%20Dal%20Loktantrik%20being%20inclined%20towards%20the%20NDA%20it%20will%20be%20eight%20votes%20short%20to%20send%20its%20eighth%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20108%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20have%20increased%20which%20needs%20111%20to%20send%20all%20its%20three%20candidates%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20two%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20one%20vote%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lone%20BSP%20MLA%20Uma%20Shankar%20Singh%20has%20not%20made%20his%20inclinations%20clear%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20to%20take%20on%20sitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-moves-to-rajya-sabha-as-congress-names-8-candidates-for-upper-house-polls%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mahajan%20who%20was%20considered%20close%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20left%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%202022.%20The%20Congress%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20assembly%2C%20while%20the%20BJP