%20put%20a%20candidate%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20file%20the%20nomination%20papers%20by%20Kupendra%20Reddy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20JD(S)%20state%20president%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20state%20can%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%20with%20five%20candidates%20vying%20for%20four%20seats%20which%20are%20up%20for%20grabs.%20The%20Congress%20earlier%20named%20three%20candidates%20including%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20G.C.%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20Syed%20Nasir%20Hussain.%20The%20BJP%20too%20earlier%20named%20Narayansa%20Bhandage%20as%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20135%20MLAs%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2066%20and%20the%20JD(S)%2019%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-six%20seats%20spread%20across%2015%20states%20will%20be%20filled%20up%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027.%20Among%20those%20retiring%20are%2028%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%3B%2011%20from%20the%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3B%20two%20each%20from%20the%20BJD%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%3B%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708091081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16190716%2FEffect-2024-02-16T190700.306.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-new-nda-candidates-close-rajya-sabha-contest-likely-in-up-himachal-karnataka%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20named%20Sanjay%20Seth%20and%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20respectively%2C%20while%20JD(S)%2C%20BJP's%20ally%2C%20named%20D.%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20from%20Karnataka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng