0gardeners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20the%20International%20Waterlily%20and%20Water%20Gardening%20Society%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20discovered%20my%20people.%20Members%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311245%2F10-social-media-travel-groups-in-india-to-plan-backpacking-solo-trip-treks-adventure-itinerary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20groups%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20different%20countries%20across%20the%20oceans%20have%20stayed%20in%20touch%20with%20me%20ever%20since.%20They%20would%20offer%20guidance%20through%20video%20calls%2C%20advising%20me%20on%20whether%20my%20actions%20were%20right%20or%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20early%20days%20when%20she%20started%20growing%20water%20flowers%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20hardy%20water%20lilies%2C%20which%20was%20a%20mistake.%20The%20kind%20was%20not%20able%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20weather%20of%20Kerala%2C%20and%20all%20the%20plants%20died.%20But%20the%20whole%20process%20motivated%20me%20to%20try%20again%20as%20I%20was%20now%20curious%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20they%20grow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20not%20only%20learned%20the%20right%20way%20of%20growing%20lilies%2C%20she%20mastered%20it.%20Presently%2C%20she%20grows%20more%20than%20100%20varieties%20of%20lilies%20in%20her%20home%20garden.%20But%20that%20was%20also%20not%20enough%20for%20her%3B%20she%20wanted%20to%20hybridise%20her%20own%20variety!%20This%2C%20she%20thought%2C%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20fulfil%20her%20dream%20of%20contributing%20something%20creative%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20the%20International%20Waterlily%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250247%2Fgurugram-startup-bring-my-flowers-subscription-success-story-entrepreneur-delhi-