%20inches%20and%20as%20large%20as%2018%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lilies%20need%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20to%20thrive.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELilies%20need%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20to%20thrive.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20They%20love%20the%20sun!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20says%20that%20lilies%20love%20sunlight%20and%20they%20need%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20sure%20they%20get%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20many%20lily%20plants%20become%20dormant.%20Place%20your%20pots%20in%20a%20sunny%20place%20and%20see%20your%20lilies%20bloom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Natural%20fertilisers%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20providing%20the%20plants%20with%20sunlight%20and%20good%20soil%2C%20Viji%20recommends%20feeding%20them%20with%20natural%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CVermicompost%20can%20do%20