atra-tejashwi-yadav-will-be-in-driving-seat-in-bihar-says-rahul-gandhi-23335462%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMid%20Day%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20also%20interacted%20with%20farmers%2C%20a%20regular%20feature%20of%20the%20Yatra%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Mahapanchayat%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20emphasised%20job%20creation%20efforts%20and%20questioned%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20alignment%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20promised%2010%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20he%20used%20to%20mock%20at%20me%20and%20ask%20if%20I%20would%20use%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20money%20(%3Cem%3Ebaap%20ka%20paisa%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20pay%20salaries.%20But%20we%20made%20the%20tired%20(%3Cem%3Ethake%20hue%3C%2Fem%3E)%20chief%20minister%20take%20significant%20steps%20towards%20job%20creation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20nearly%2017-month%20period%20he%20shared%20power%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20use%20colourful%20epithets%20against%20him%20like%20you%20people%20are%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Nitish%20ji%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20people%2C%20who%20want%20to%20know%20under%20what%20circumstances%20he%20chose%20to%20realign%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20despite%20saying%20in%20the%20past%20that%20he%20would%20prefer%20to%20be%20consigned%20to%20dust%20%3Cem%3E(mitti%20mein%20mil%20jayenge)%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20accept%20death%20%3Cem%3E(mar%20jaana%20qabool%20hai)%3C%2Fem%3E%20rather%20than%20going%20back%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20RJD%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20saw%20protests%20against%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20political%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%5C%22%3Efaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20fin