%20embankments%20in%20Supaul%20of%20Bihar%2C%20walked%20250%20kilometres%20in%2012%20days%20to%20reach%20Patna%20to%20press%20for%20their%20long-stand%20demand%20for%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Epadyatr%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20(walkathon)%20began%20in%20Supaul%20town%E2%80%99s%20Bairiya%20Manch%20and%20crossed%20six%20districts.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20padyatra%20were%20above%20the%20age%20of%2040%20and%20some%20among%20them%20were%20even%20above%2060%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20signs%20of%20fatigue%20on%20their%20faces.%20Instead%2C%20anger%20was%20writ%20large%20on%20their%20faces%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20apathy%20to%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20distributed%20four-page%20handbills%20en%20route%20to%20the%20people%20who%20they%20encountered%20during%20the%20padyatra.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20distributed%2040%2C000%20handbills%20to%20the%20people%20to%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20Kosi%20people%E2%80%99s%20plight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pratap%20Kumar%2C%20in%20his%2020s%2C%20says.%20His%20land%20falls%20within%20embankments%20and%20he%20faces%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20crop%20almost%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20padyatra%20started%20on%20January%2030%20and%20reached%20Gardanibagh%2C%20in%20Patna%20on%20February%2012%20noon%2C%20where%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20Prafulla%20Samantra%2C%20Sunilam%2C%20and%20other%20renowned%20activists%20addressed%20the%20padyatra%20and%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16155802%2FPXL_20240212_090802581-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16155802%2FPXL_20240212_090802581-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16155802%2FPXL_20240212_090802581-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16155802%2FPXL_20240212_090802581-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMedha%20Patkar%2C%20Dr.%20Sunilam%2C%20Mahendra%20Yadav%20and%20other%20activists%20holding%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20Committee%20report.%20Photo%3A%20Umesh%20Kumar%20Ray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20a%20dozen%20committees%20were%20formed%20since%20the%20embankments%20came%20into%20being%20on%20the%20Kosi%20river%2C%20but%20their%20recommendations%20were%20never%20implemented.%20We%20have%20also%20formed%20a%20public%20commission%20and%20submitted%20the%20report%20to%20the%20government%2C%20but%20the%20government%20is%20not%20paying%20any%20attention%20to%20the%20victims%2C%E2%80%9D%20Medha%20Patkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBasic%20facilities%20like%20health%2C%20road%2C%20water%2C%20education%20are%20constitutional%20rights%20of%20people%20but%20the%20government%20has%20snatched%20these%20rights%20from%20Kosi%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Supaul%20district%20and%20participant%20in%20the%20padyatra%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHumara%20ghar%20tatbandh%20ke%20beech%20hai%E2%80%A6barish%20ke%20samay%20hum%20log%20sadme%20mein%20rahte%20hain%20ki%20kab%20badh%20aayega%20aur%20humko%20ujad%20dega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(our%20house%20is%20within%20Kosi%20embankments%E2%80%A6.we%20live%20in%20fear%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20because%20floods%20can%20damage%20our%20house%20anytime).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20first%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20first%20president%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20had%20proposed%20embankments%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20Kosi%20river%2C%20they%20had%20promised%20that%20they%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20But%20the%20government%20left%20us%20in%20a%20lurch.%20No%20government%20facilities%20reach%20us.%20We%20have%20no%20school%2C%20no%20hospital%2C%20no%20road%20and%20drinking%20water%20within%20embankments%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chandra%20Mohan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkosi-river-embankments-bihar%5C%22%3ENot%20Everyone%20Is%20Happy%20With%20New%20Embankments%20on%20the%20Kosi%20in%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecades%20of%20sufferings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKosi%20river%2C%20which%20originates%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20flows%20260%20kilometres%20in%20Bihar.%20It%20joins%20the%20Ganga%20river%20near%20Kursela%20in%20the%20Katihar%20district.%20The%20river%20causes%20floods%20almost%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sixties%2C%20to%20limit%20the%20spread%20of%20this%20river%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20build%20embankments%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20river%2C%20when%20the%20Kosi%20Plan%201953%20came%20into%20being.%20In%201955%2C%20a%20foundation%20stone%20was%20laid%20to%20construct%20embankments%20and%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20construction%20was%20completed.%20About%208%20lakh%20people%20from%20380%20villages%20of%20four%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20Supaul%2C%20Saharsa%2C%20Madhubani%20and%20Darbhanga%20were%20trapped%20within%20two%20embankments%20and%20they%20were%20demanding%20their%20relocation%20as%20they%20were%20going%20to%20face%20the%20wrath%20of%20Kosi%20as%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20water%20spread%20area%20was%20compressed%20in%20few%20kilometers%20by%20constructing%20embankments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20anger%20grew%2C%20the%20government%20decided%20to%20relocate%20the%20families%20trapped%20within%20embankments.%20People%20were%20promised%20that%20they%20would%20be%20given%20land%20outside%20the%20embankment%20to%20make%20houses%2C%20but%20many%20families%20did%20not%20get%20the%20land.%20And%2C%20those%20who%20got%20land%20for%20houses%20outside%20the%20embankments%20returned%20to%20be%20within%20embankments%20as%20their%20agricultural%20lands%20were%20within%20embankments%20and%20their%20relocated%20lands%20were%20occupied%20by%20mafias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20that%20earlier%20when%20there%20were%20no%20embankments%20on%20the%20Kosi%20river%2C%20huge%20waters%20coming%20in%20the%20river%20would%20spread%20in%20large%20areas%20so%20flood%20impact%20was%20less%20and%20water%20would%20recede%20in%20just%20a%20few%20days.%20But%20after%20embankments%2C%20the%20river%20water%20remains%20confined%20to%20a%20few%20kilometres%2C%20so%20its%20impact%20has%20increased%20manifold.%20Now%20people%20face%20flood%20and%20erosion%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20another%20farmer%20who%20is%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20pucca%20houses%20as%20they%20can%20washed%20away%20anytime%20into%20the%20river.%20So%20we%20make%20temporary%20houses.%20A%20house%20does%20not%20last%20even%20for%20five%20years%20and%20it%20gets%20destroyed%20in%20the%20Kosi%20floods.%20We%20are%20living%20in%20trouble%20inside%20Kosi%2C%20but%20the%20government%20is%20not%20concerned%20about%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGayatri%20Devi%2C%2060%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20year%20our%20house%20gets%20destroyed%20in%20floods.%20The%20grains%20kept%20at%20home%20get%20wasted%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20even%20get%20any%20compensation.%20We%20have%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20refugees%20on%20our%20own%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20we%20want%20from%20the%20government%20is%20to%20give%20us%20land%20outside%20the%20Kosi%20embankment%20so%20that%20we%20can%20be%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkoshi-river-avulsion-sedimentation-embankments-bihar-floods%2F%5C%22%3EA%20Story%20in%20Images%3A%20Why%20Does%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Koshi%20River%20Change%20Course%20So%20Often%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20Yadav%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Kosi%20Navnirman%20Manch%20(KNM)%2C%20who%20organised%20the%20%3Cem%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20living%20within%20the%20embankments%20are%20living%20miserable%20lives%20for%20decades%20but%20they%20are%20being%20neglected%20by%20the%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20four%20demands%20from%20the%20government.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20the%20government%20must%20conduct%20a%20new%20survey%20to%20find%20out%20the%20families%20who%20were%20not%20rehabilitated%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20embankments%20and%20they%20should%20be%20rehabilitated%20properly%20outside%20the%20embankments.%20Those%20who%20were%20displaced%20due%20to%20Kosi%20erosion%20and%20now%20living%20on%20the%20embankments%20should%20also%20be%20rehabilitated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160100%2FPXL_20240212_054132268-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160100%2FPXL_20240212_054132268-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160100%2FPXL_20240212_054132268-1-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160100%2FPXL_20240212_054132268-1-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKosi%20people%20living%20within%20embankments%20demanded%20rehabilitation%20as%20they%20face%20floods%20and%20erosion%20from%20Kosi%20river.%20Photo%3A%20Umesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20KPVP%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20the%20Chandra%20Kishor%20Pathak%20Committee%20was%20formed%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20rehabilitation%20plan%20for%20Kosi%20victims.%20The%20committee%20has%20formed%20Kosi%20Pidit%20Vikas%20Pradhikar%20(Kosi%20Victim%20Development%20Authority)%20and%20proposed%2017%20points%20of%20recommendations%20including%20reservation%20for%20Kosi%20victims%20in%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Mahendra%20Yadav%20filed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainmedia.in%2Fdid-bihar-government-misled-court-on-kosi-case%2F%5C%22%3EPublic%20interest%20litigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20in%20this%20regard.%20Patna%20high%20court%20in%20its%20order%20had%20asked%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Pathak%20Committee%20and%20whether%20the%20recommendations%20of%20that%20report%20had%20been%20implemented%20or%20not.%20The%20Bihar%20government%20had%20asked%20for%20eight%20weeks%E2%80%99%20time%20to%20submit%20the%20report%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20eight%20weeks%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20told%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20that%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Pathak%20Committee%20was%20not%20with%20the%20Water%20Resources%20Department.%20The%20Bihar%20government%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Water%20Resources%20Department%20is%20trying%20to%20obtain%20the%20Pathak%20Committee%20report%20and%20find%20out%20what%20actions%20were%20taken%20on%20that%20report.%20The%20state%20government%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20letter%20had%20been%20written%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20the%20district%20concerned%20for%20the%20report%2C%20but%20it%20could%20not%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reporter%20has%20accessed%20the%20Pathak%20committee%20report.%20Chandra%20Kishore%20Pathak%20in%20his%20report%20wrote%20in%20detail%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20people%20living%20within%20Kosi%20embankments.%20The%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20assurances%20given%20to%20these%20people%20living%20between%20the%20embankments%20of%20Kosi%20have%20not%20been%20fulfilled%20till%20date.%20Their%20suffering%20could%20not%20be%20alleviated%2C%20making%20their%20condition%20extremely%20miserable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20incomplete%20and%20impractical%20rehabilitation%20plans%20were%20made%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20they%20failed.%20The%20Committee%20feels%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sacred%20duty%20and%20great%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Government%20to%20take%20vigorous%20steps%20for%20the%20economic%20development%20and%20livelihood%20of%20these%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20Yadav%20demanded%20that%20KPVP%20should%20be%20activated%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20KPVP%20is%20widely%20available.%20The%20government%20must%20activate%20it%20and%20implement%20its%20recommendations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20started%20conducting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2022%2F05%2Fas-kosi-river-keep-changing-ownership-of-land-on-its-embankments-under-question%2F%5C%22%3Eland%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20new%20survey%20rule%2C%20if%20the%20river%20is%20flowing%20through%20farmland%2C%20the%20land%20in%20question%20goes%20to%20the%20state%20government.%20And%20those%20parts%20which%20were%20submerged%20by%20the%20river%20in%20the%20cadastral%20survey%20but%20later%20reappeared%20due%20to%20changes%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20river%20then%20that%20land%20would%20also%20become%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%203.5%20lakh%20acres%20of%20land%20falls%20between%20the%20two%20embankments%20of%20Kosi.%20If%20the%20government%20goes%20by%20its%20rule%2C%20then%20all%20the%20lands%20should%20become%20the%20Bihar%20government%E2%80%99s%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20are%20opposing%20this%20decision.%20They%20say%20that%20Kosi%20changes%20its%20course%20very%20fast%2C%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20all%20the%20land%20of%20the%20farmers%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20do%20land%20survey%20according%20to%20its%20own%20rule%2C%20then%20it%20should%20give%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20land%20outside%20the%20embankments%20to%20all%20the%20landowners%20whose%20land%20is%20inside%20the%20embankment%20instead%20of%20farms%20or%20give%20compensation%20equal%20to%20the%20fertile%20land%20outside%20the%20embankment%20at%20today%E2%80%99s%20rate.%20If%20the%20government%20does%20not%20do%20this%20immediately%2C%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20land%20on%20which%20the%20river%20is%20flowing%20should%20be%20with%20actual%20landowners%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahendra%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708081212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16155513%2FEffect-2024-02-16T155448.872.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbihar-families-affected-by-kosi-river-floods-march-12-days-to-patna-to-lodge-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%208%20lakh%20people%20living%20between%20embankments%20across%20the%20river%2C%20which%20is%20spread%20over%20Supaul%2C%20Saharsa%2C%20Madhubani%20and%20Darbhanga%20districts%2C%20suffer%20losses%20every%20year%20due%20to%20floods.%20They%20have%20been%20demanding%20rehabilitation%20for%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbihar-families-affected-by-kosi-river-floods-march-12-days-to-patna-to-lodge-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singapore%20has%20'done%20deal%20so%20Taylor%20Swift%20can't%20perform%20in%20any%20other%20countries%20in%20southeast%20Asia'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708080960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-taylor-swift-golden-globes_6434515.jpg%3F20240127184620%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsingapore-has-done-deal-so-taylor-swift-cant-perform-in-any-other-countries-in-southeast-asia-13072902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore%20has%20done%20a%20deal%20to%20ensure%20Taylor%20Swift%20doesn't%20perform%20anywhere%20else%20in%20southeast%20Asia%2C%20Thailand's%20prime%20minister%20has%20claimed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsingapore-has-done-deal-so-taylor-swift-cant-perform-in-any-other-countries-in-southeast-asia-13072902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsingapore-has-done-deal-so-taylor-swift-cant-perform-in-any-other-countries-in-southeast-asia-13072902%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsingapore-has-done-deal-so-taylor-swift-cant-perform-in-any-other-countries-in-southeast-asia-13072902%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'MSP%20Applies%20to%20Only%2010%25%20of%20Agri%20Households%2C%20Hike%20Will%20Raise%20Food%20Inflation%20by%2025-30%25'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160448%2FKT-16-B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20agriculture%20experts%2C%20professor%20Ashok%20Gulati%2C%20discusses%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clearly%20spoke%20out%20against%20making%20MSP%20legally%20binding%20as%20well%20as%20calculating%20it%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20C2%2B50%25%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGulati%20said%20only%2010%25%20of%20agricultural%20households%20sell%20crops%20under%20the%20MSP%20regime.%20He%20said%20the%2023%20crops%2C%20for%20whom%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20MSP%20be%20made%20legally%20binding%2C%20only%20constitute%2027.8%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20agricultural%20produce.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20MSP%20regime%20for%20wheat%20and%20rice%20applies%20to%20some%20six%20or%20seven%20states%2C%20of%20which%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20are%20new%20entries%2C%20and%20largely%20excludes%20most%20of%20east%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2040-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20professor%20Gulati%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Infosys%20Professor%20for%20Agriculture%20at%20ICRIER%20and%20former%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Commission%20for%20Agricultural%20Costs%20and%20Prices%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20high-flying%20sectors%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%20such%20as%20poultry%2C%20which%20is%20growing%20at%208-9%25%2C%20fisheries%20at%207-8%25%2C%20and%20milk%20at%205-6%25%2C%20do%20not%20depend%20upon%20any%20MSP%20regime%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20to%20improve%20the%20income%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20making%20MSP%20legally%20binding%20would%20be%20anti-farmer.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20ramifications%20and%20consequences%20of%20calculating%20MSP%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20formula%20of%20C2%20%2B%2050%25.%20It%20will%20increase%20food%20prices%20by%2025-30%25%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20discussed%20how%20farmers%20should%20be%20supported%2C%20either%20through%20some%20form%20of%20a%20price%20stabilisation%20fund%2C%20so%20that%20when%20market%20prices%20fall%20below%20the%20MSP%20levels%2C%20the%20government%20makes%20up%20the%20difference%2C%20or%20preferably%2C%20through%20an%20income%20support%20scheme%2C%20which%20is%20the%20practice%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20he%20explained%20how%20the%20real%20incomes%20of%20farmers%20can%20be%20improved.%20At%20present%2C%20the%20incomes%20are%20only%20modestly%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20incentivising%20farmers%20to%20shift%20from%20wheat%20and%20rice%20to%20high-value%20agricultural%20produce%2C%20such%20as%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20livestock%20and%20fisheries.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20not%20imposing%20arbitrary%20export%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20the%20need%20for%20the%20government%20to%20move%20away%20from%20its%20pro-consumer%20bias%2C%20where%20they%20protect%20non-agricultural%20households%20against%20inflation%2C%20and%20create%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20which%20is%20more%20equal%20in%20handling%20farmer%20interests%20as%20well%20as%20consumer%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20addressed%20the%20trust%20deficit%20that%20has%20emerged%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20between%20the%20government%20and%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FiIwcv7walvY%3Fsi%3Da0AkvvagASBgiFmV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708079791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16160448%2FKT-16-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-msp-applies-to-only-10-of-agri-households-hike-will-raise-food-inflation-by-25-30%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20professor%20Ashok%20Gulati%20spoke%20about%20the%20ramifications%20and%20conseque