ent%20on%20unauthorised%20Hindu%20religious%20structures%20in%20forest%20and%20%3Cem%3Enazul%3C%2Fem%3E%20lands%E2%80%9D%20(a%20type%20of%20government%20land%20used%20for%20non-agricultural%20and%20public%20purpose%20such%20as%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20building%2C%20road%2C%20market%20and%20playground).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20finding%20team%20visited%20Haldwani%20on%20February%2014%20and%20prepared%20the%20interim%20report%20based%20on%20the%20conversations%20with%20civil%20society%20members%2C%20journalists%2C%20writers%20and%20lawyers%20and%20telephonic%20conversations%20with%20a%20few%20affected%20persons%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEviction%20stayed%20by%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20several%20disputes%20arose%20regarding%20the%20legal%20ownership%20of%20tracts%20of%20urban%20land%20in%20Muslim%20majority%20areas%20in%20Haldwani.%20While%20Muslims%20who%20occupy%20these%20lands%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20rightful%20lessees%2C%20the%20state%20government%20suggests%20that%20these%20are%20government%20lands%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20proposed%20eviction%20related%20to%C2%A0the%20claims%20by%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20regarding%20settlements%20in%20Railway%20land%20occupied%20by%20Muslim%20residents%20in%20Haldwani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bulldozers%20were%20out%20while%20matter%20was%20sub-judice%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20is%20related%20to%20around%20six%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20which%20a%2020-year-old%20mosque%20and%20a%20madrasa%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20masjid%20and%20madrasa%20were%20sealed%20by%20the%20local%20municipality%20on%20February%204%20after%20a%20group%20of%20%3Cem%3Eulemas%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20the%20municipality%20officials%20to%20plead%20against%20the%20eviction%20notices%20served%20on%20January%2030%20to%20vacate%20both%20the%20mosque%20and%20madrasa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20police%20asserted%20that%20the%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20government%20while%20Sofiya%20Malik%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20lessee%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%20approached%20the%20Uttarakhand%20High%20Court%20due%20to%20these%20recent%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20judge%20bench%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20February%208%20and%20the%20next%20hearing%20was%20on%20February%2014.%20The%20local%20residents%20told%20the%20fact%20finding%20team%20that%20on%20February%208%20evening%20the%20local%20officers%20arrived%20with%20bulldozers%2C%20municipal%20workers%20and%20significant%20police%20protection%20to%20undertake%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20the%20madrasa%20%E2%80%9Cdespite%20the%20matter%20being%20sub-judice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-a-150-year-old-ploy-to-incite-religious-violence-is-still-used-in-india%5C%22%3EHow%20a%20150-Year-Old%20Ploy%20to%20Incite%20Religious%20Violence%20Is%20Still%20Used%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20anger%20fuelled%20as%20women%20were%20beaten%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20fact%20finding%20report%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%20residents%20who%20stood%20before%20the%20bulldozers%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20prevent%20the%20demolitions%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtarakhand-violence-erupts-in-haldwani-after-madrasa-demolition-shoot-at-sight-orders-issued%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20forcefully%20removed%2C%20dragged%20and%20beaten%20by%20male%20and%20female%20police%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20angered%20the%20local%20community.%20Moreover%2C%20their%20plea%20that%20the%20Quran%20and%20other%20sacred%20pro