0forces%20including%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20is%20responding%20appropriately%20by%20firing%20tear%20gas%20shells%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%20Things%20are%20under%20watch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Imphal-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheFrontierManipur%3Fref%3Dembed_page%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Frontier%20Manipur%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20four%20photographs%20on%20February%2016%20morning%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CChurachandpur%20DC%20(deputy%20commissioner)%20office%20was%20burnt%20down%20by%20Kuki%20militants%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20confirm%20this%20news%20independently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmob-storms-sp-office-in-manipurs-churachandpur-after-head-constable-from-kuki-zo-community-was-suspended%2Farticle67850970.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%2C%20one%20person%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20security%20forces%20and%20several%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20SP%20office%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20public%20anger%20was%20due%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20head%20constable%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%20Siamlalpaul%20was%20posted%20at%20the%20Churachandpur%20police%20station.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-mob-fury-in-churachandpur-after-cop-suspension%5C%22%3EImphal-based%20news%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20action%20against%20him%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D%20after%20a%20viral%20video%20clip%20featuring%20him%20was%20circulated.%20It%20allegedly%20showed%20him%20making%20a%20video%20with%20%E2%80%9Carmed%20miscreants%20sitting%20together%20with%20village%20volunteers%E2%80%9D%20from%20his%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20order%20issued%20by%20Churachandpur%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Shivanand%20Surve%20noted%20that%20Siamlalpaul%20was%20found%20culpable%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20misconduct%E2%80%9D%20in%20spite%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmember%20of%20a%20disciplined%20force%E2%80%9D%20under%20Rule%2066%2C%20Part%203%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Manual.%20The%20order%20said%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20could%20be%20initiated%20against%20him%20and%20that%20he%20could%20not%20leave%20the%20station%20without%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20SP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20order%20is%20said%20to%20have%20led%20the%20mob%20to%20storm%20the%20SP%20and%20DC%20offices%20in%20Churachandpur.%20The%20mob%20ended%20up%20vandalising%20the%20public%20offices.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESix%20held%20for%20arms%20loot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20state%20police%20has%20arrested%20six%20persons%20in%20the%20arms%20looting%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20on%20February%2013%20at%20the%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRBn)%20camp%20in%20Chingarel%20area%20of%20Imphal%20East%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20Police%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20X%20on%20February%2014%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20of%20arms%20looting%20case%20of%205th%20IRBn%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%20by%20an%20unruly%20mob%20on%20the%20night%20of%2013.02.2024%2C%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20arrested%20six%20persons%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20and%20they%20have%20been%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20by%20a%20judicial%20magistrate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFour%20Insas%20rifles%2C%20one%20AK%20Ghatak%2C%20two%20magazines%20of%20SLR%2C%20and%2016%20small%20boxes%20of%209mm%20ammunition%20looted%20from%20the%20IRBn%20camp%20have%20also%20been%20recovered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fmanipur-6-arrested-for-looting-arms-from-irbn-camp%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20police%20did%20not%20mention%20from%20where%20the%20arms%20were%20recovered%2C%20or%20from%20where%20the%20persons%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20after%20the%20IRBn%20mob%20attack%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20l%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Earge%20number%E2%80%9D%20of%20village%20volunteers%20also%20attempted%20to%20barge%20into%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20Training%20College%20at%20Pangei%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20located%20around%205%20kms%20from%20Chingarel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20X%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2013%2C%20in%20order%20to%20repel%20violent%20mobs%2C%20including%20armed%20miscreants%2C%20trying%20to%20storm%20MPTC%2C%20Pangei%2C%20security%20forces%20resorted%20to%20the%20use%20of%20legal%20force.%20During%20the%20incident%2C%20one%20person%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%20and%20three%20persons%20sustained%20injuries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20suspended%20seven%20IRBn%20personnel%20over%20the%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Commandant%20of%205th%20IRB%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20H.%20Balram%20Singh%20in%20an%20order%20said%20the%20seven%20personnel%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20until%20further%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-mob-fury-in-churachandpur-after-cop-suspension%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20this%20move%20too%20was%20taken%20under%20Rule%2066%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Manual%20Part-3%2C%20and%20that%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20may%20be%20initiated%20against%20them%20too%20for%20negligence%20and%20dereliction%20of%20duty.%20All%20suspended%20personnel%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20camp%20without%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20station%20commandant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708074920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16145341%2FGGBKaMkWoAEYCW5.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attacks%20have%20seen%20large%20mobs%20barge%20into%20police%20stations%20or%20armouries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madeleine%20McCann%20suspect%20in%20court%20on%20unrelated%20charges%20-%20as%20his%20lawyer%20gets%20judge%20thrown%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708073820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-mccann-christian-b_6457527.jpg%3F20240216102258%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchristian-b-suspect-in-madeleine-mccanns-disappearance-appears-in-court-accused-of-unrelated-sex-offences-13072804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prime%20suspect%20in%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Madeleine%20McCann%20is%20appearing%20in%20a%20German%20court%2C%20where%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20unrelated%20sex%20offences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C